casebody.data:
Antwon Rashad MYRICK, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3642 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 19, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The mandate in 2D12-4235 having issued on May 19, 2014, this petition alleging ineffective assistance of appellate counsel is dismissed as untimely. See Fla. R. App. P. 9.141(d)(5).

LaROSE, C.J., and MORRIS and SALARIO, JJ., Concur.
